elements.2211.03076_3c2ee4244630ee3684a0f2df9d1e2: PROPs and PROBs are categories used to encode structures borne by objects in symmetric and braided monoidal categories respectively, whilst crossed simplicial groups are categories which encode a unital, associative multiplication and a compatible group action
